Class PlaceOrderController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.spuranik.web.BaseController
      • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.spuranik.web.PlaceOrderController

  • public class PlaceOrderController
extends BaseController
    PlaceOrder Controller extending Base Controller consists of enterprise bean, post construct Along with method to createproductfororder, createorder Used to create an product for order and also a method to get address and mobile number when item is added to cart
